org.hardroid.common

Class ActivityRecognitionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hardroid.common.ActivityRecognitionResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class ActivityRecognitionResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Results of an activity recognition prediction. Contains a list of predicted activities that the user might be doing during a period of time. The Activities are sorted by most probable activities
